    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go with plenty of life left in it! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale, so I\u2019ve set a really fair price for such a solid vehicle. Shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 28500.0,
