    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a dependable daily driver and a well-preserved enthusiast car. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, expected road wear that comes with careful ownership. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the leather upholstery remains supple and the dashboard is free of cracks or fading. All onboard electronics, including the premium sound system and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. We recently installed a fresh set of all-season tires and performed a full brake service, ensuring it's road-ready from day one. The engine runs quiet and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. It\u2019s a complete package for someone who wants quality without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
